        <abstract> 
<p>Has enjoyed FWF’s volume [<hi rend="italic">Chapters on language</hi>]. Had found Max Müller’s theory obscure and weak.</p> 
            <p>Believes FWF would come to agree with him on species if he studied general questions in natural history. To argue for immutability of species on the basis of geology resembles a wise savage in a nation with no books saying his language has never changed.</p>
        </abstract>
